  "title": "Bad Gut",
  "description": "a show about comedian Elyott Ryan's journey through severe health issues and his road to recovery. As a teenager, his body was a mess—crippling stomach aches, insomnia, chronic fatigue and he could even get drunk off sugar. Now, he's ready to share the wild, weird, and funny lessons he learned from living with a unwell body.",
